lass=\"wp-block-heading\">Insert template<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you created the template, you will be able to use and insert them into the editor content easily.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While on the <strong>Templates tab<\/strong>, for the template you want to insert, <strong>click the Insert button<\/strong>, the template content will be automatically injected into the contract editor.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In order to make the contract process creation easier, in Perfex CRM you can create predefined HTML templates that can be used each time a contract is created. Create contract template You can create a contract template while viewing the contract by clicking on the Templates tab and then click on the Add Template button. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3142","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-contracts"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3142","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3142"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3142\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3142"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3142"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com